i || [[N. Lingusamy]] || ||\n|-\n| ''[[Sarkar (2018 film)|Sarkar]]'' || Nila || [[AR Murugadoss]] || ||\n|-\n| 2019 || ''[[Manmadhudu 2]]'' || Suma || [[Rahul Ravindran]] || rowspan='2'|Telugu || Cameo appearance ||\n|-\n| rowspan=\"7\"|2020 ||  scope=\"row\" style=\"background:#FFFFCC;\"|  ''[[Miss India (film)|Miss India]]'' {{dagger}} || {{TBA}} || Narendra Nath  ||  post production ||<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.thenewsminute.com/article/watch-keerthy-suresh-all-style-miss-india-teaser-107861%3famp|title=Watch: Keerthy Suresh is all style in 'Miss India' teaser|date=26 August 2019|website=The News Minute|archive-url=|archive-date=|url-status=|access-date=2019-08-31}}</ref>\n|- \n|scope=\"row\" style=\"background:#FFFFCC;\"|  ''[[Marakkar: Arabikadalinte Simham]]'' {{dagger}} || Aarcha || [[Priyadarshan]] || Malayalam ||  post production || \n|-\n| scope=\"row\" style=\"background:#FFFFCC;\"|  ''Penguin'' {{dagger}} || {{TBA}} || Eshwar || Tamil || post production ||<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.pinkvilla.com/entertainment/south/penguin-shoot-wrap-keerthy-suresh-gets-emotional-she-talks-about-sweet-and-memorable-journey-483494|title= Penguin shoot wrap up: Keerthy Suresh gets emotional as she talks about the sweet and memorable journey|date=3 November 2019|website=Pinkvilla| archive-url=|archive-date=|url-status=|access-date=2019-11-04}}</ref>\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" style=\"background:#FFFFCC;\"|''[[Good Luck Sakhi]] '' {{dagger}} || Sakhi || [[Nagesh Kukunoor]] || rowspan=\"2\"|Telugu||Filming ||<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.indiatoday.in/amp/movies/regional-cinema/story/keerthy-suresh-plays-a-sharpshooter-in-nagesh-kukunoor-s-good-luck-sakhi-1614134-2019-10-30|title=Keerthy Suresh plays a sharpshooter in Nagesh Kukunoor's 'Good Luck Sakhi'|date=30 October 2019|website=India Today| archive-url=|archive-date=|url-status=|access-date=2019-11-10}}</ref>\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" style=\"background:#FFFFCC;\"| ''Rang De'' {{dagger}} || Anu || Venky Atluri || Filmi