g in Season 1. -->\n* [[Harriet Walter]] as [[Clementine Churchill]]<ref name=\"finalreel\">{{cite web |url=http://www.finalreel.co.uk/the-crown-trailer-peter-morgan-netflix/ |title=The Crown trailer: First look at Peter Morgan's Netflix drama |website=Final Reel |last=Lloyd |first=Kenji |date= 7 January 2016 |accessdate=7 January 2016}}</ref> <!-- 101 102 104 105 106 107 -->\n* [[Nicholas Rowe (actor)|Nicholas Rowe]] as [[Jock Colville]]<ref name=\"geeksofdoom\" /> <!-- 101 102 103 104 105 106 107 108 109 -->\n* [[Simon Chandler]] as [[Clement Attlee]] <!-- 101 102 104 105 109 -->\n* [[Kate Phillips]] as Venetia Scott <!-- 101 102 104 -->\n* [[Ronald Pickup]] as the [[Geoffrey Fisher|Archbishop of Canterbury]] <!-- 101 103 105 110 -->\n* Nigel Cooke as [[Harry Crookshank]] <!-- 101 102 104 109 -->\n* [[Patrick Drury]] as the [[Roger Lumley, 11th Earl of Scarbrough|Lord Chamberlain]] <!-- 101 102 103 105 106 -->\n* [[John Woodvine]] as the [[Cyril Garbett|Archbishop of York]] <!-- 101 103 105 110 -->\n* [[Jo Stone-Fewings]] as Collins <!-- 104 109 -->\n* [[Tony Guilfoyle]] as the [[Michael Ramsey|Bishop of Durham]] <!-- 105 110 -->\n* Paul Thornley as Bill Mattheson <!-- 106 110 -->\n{{div col end}}\n\n====Season 2====<!-- List of NAMED characters recurring in season 2. -->\n{{Div col|colwidth=35em}}\n* [[Chloe Pirrie]] as Eileen Parker <!-- 201 202 203 -->\n* [[Nicholas Burns (actor)|Nicholas Burns]] as [[Anthony Nutting]] <!-- 201 203 -->\n* [[Lucy Russell (actress)|Lucy Russell]] as [[Edwina Mountbatten, Countess Mountbatten of Burma|Lady Mountbatten]] <!-- 201 202 204 -->\n* Richard Elfyn as [[Selwyn Lloyd]] <!-- 201 203 206 207 -->\n* [[Adrian Lukis]] as Vice-Admiral Sir [[Conolly Abel Smith]] <!-- 202 203 -->\n* Guy Williams as [[Prince Andrew of Greece and Denmark]] <!-- 202 209 -->\n* [[Simon Paisley Day]] as Meryn Lewis <!-- 202 203 -->\n* [[Sylvestra Le Touzel]] as [[Lady Dorothy Macmillan|Dorothy Macmillan]] <!-- 204 205 208 210 -->\n* Catherine Bailey as