te List|website=[[Variety (magazine)|Variety]]|first=Adam|last=B. Vary|date=January 18, 2020|accessdate=January 19, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" | [[26th Screen Actors Guild Awards|Screen Actors Guild Awards]]\n| Outstanding Performance by an Ensemble in a Drama Series\n| [[Marion Bailey]], Helena Bonham Carter, Olivia Colman, [[Charles Dance]], [[Ben Daniels]], [[Erin Doherty]], [[Charles Edwards (English actor)|Charles Edwards]], Tobias Menzies, [[Josh O'Connor]], [[Sam Phillips (actor)|Sam Phillips]], [[David Rintoul]] and [[Jason Watkins (actor)|Jason Watkins]]\n| {{won}}\n|  rowspan=\"3\" |<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.sagawards.org/media/news/releases/nominations-announced-26th-annual-screen-actors-guild-awards-%C2%AE |title=NOMINATIONS ANNOUNCED FOR THE 26TH ANNUAL SCREEN ACTORS GUILD AWARDS |date=December 11, 2019 |accessdate=December 11, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | Outstanding Performance by a Female Actor in a Drama Series\n| Helena Bonham Carter\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| Olivia Colman\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| [[Costume Designers Guild Awards 2019|Costume Designers Guild Awards]]\n| Excellence in Period Television\n| Amy Roberts <small>(for \"Cri De Coeur\")</small>\n| {{nom}}\n|<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/lists/2020-costume-designers-guild-awards-full-list-nominations-1259668 |title=Costume Designers Guild Awards: 'Hustlers,' 'Rocketman' Among Nominees |website=The Hollywood Reporter |first=Lindsay |last=Weinberg |date=December 10, 2019 |accessdate=January 11, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[18th Visual Effects Society Awards|Visual Effects Society Awards]]\n| [[Visual Effects Society Award for Outstanding Supporting Visual Effects in a Photoreal Episode|Outstanding Supporting Visual Effects in a Photoreal Episode]]\n| Ben Turner, Reece Ewing, David Fleet and Jonathan Wood <small>(for \"Aberfan\")</small>\n| {{nom}}\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2020/01/ves-awards-nominations-2020-list-the-lion-king-the-mandalorian-game-of-t